server-updates-received = Update has been received, server will automatically restart for update at the end of this round.
server-updates-shutdown = Server is shutting down for update and will automatically restart.
server-updates-shutdown-uptime = Server is shutting down for periodic cleanup and will automatically restart.
server-updates-shutdown-rounds = Server is shutting down for periodic cleanup after reaching its round limit and will automatically restart.
server-updates-shutdown-scheduled = Server is shutting down for its scheduled restart and will automatically restart.
server-updates-scheduled-restart-pending = The scheduled restart time has been reached. The server will restart at the end of the round.
server-updates-scheduled-restart-round-end = The server will restart for its scheduled maintenance shortly. It will be back up right away - see you in a moment!
